<template>
  <transition name="slide-fade">
    <slot />
  </transition>

<style lang="scss" scoped>
.slide-fade-enter-active {
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.slide-fade-leave-active {
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(1, 0.5, 0.8, 1);
}
.slide-fade-enter,
.slide-fade-leave-to {
  transform: translateX(10px);
  opacity: 0;
}
